'''達倫·傑佛瑞·比提'''（{{lang-en|Darren Jeffrey Beattie}}）是[[美國|美國]]學者和作家，曾是[[杜克大學|杜克大學]]客座講師、於[[唐納川普|川普]]任內在[[白宮|白宮]]擔任過演講稿撰寫人。亦為新聞網站《左輪手槍新聞》（Revolver News）的創始人<ref>{{cite news |title=Beattie Responds To ‘Dirtbag’ Smear By CNN’s Cuomo Over Revolver’s 1/6 Report, Mocks ‘Titty Ring Brother’ And ‘Disgraced Father’ |url=https://nationalfile.com/darren-beattie-responds-to-dirtbag-smear-by-unhinged-cnn-anchor-chris-cuomo/ |accessdate=2021-06-19 |publisher=National File |date=2021-06-17}}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
比提擁有杜克大學的政治理論博士學位。他曾擔任杜克大學的客座講師<ref name=":0">{{Cite news|title=Matt Gaetz Hires Speechwriter Fired From White House Over White Nationalist Conference|url=https://www.thedailybeast.com/matt-gaetz-hires-dr-darren-beattie-speechwriter-fired-from-white-house-over-white-nationalist-conference|newspaper=The Daily Beast|date=2019-04-19|accessdate=2021-02-05|language=en|first=Sam Brodey,Sam|last=Stein}}</ref>。

2016年，他是一百多位簽名支持[[唐納·川普|唐納·川普]][[2016年唐納·川普競選美國總統|競選總統]]的學者和作家之一<ref>{{Cite web|title=Professor who predicted Trump's win explains how he knew, what comes next|url=https://www.dukechronicle.com/article/2016/11/professor-who-predicted-trumps-win-explains-how-he-knew-what-comes-next|accessdate=2021-02-05|date=2016-11-11|publisher=The Chronicle|language=en}}</ref>。2016年11月，他在選舉日前成功地預測川普將會勝選<ref>{{Cite web|title=What Can We Expect on Nov. 8, and After?|url=https://today.duke.edu/2016/11/what-can-we-expect-nov-8-and-after|accessdate=2021-02-05|date=2016-11-02|publisher=Duke Today|language=en}}</ref>。

川普任內，比提一度在白宮擔任政策助理和演講稿撰寫人。由於比提早前曾在2016年參加過H·L·孟肯俱樂部（H.L. Mencken Club）的一場年度會議，而一些[[白人民族主義|白人民族主義]]者也參加了該場會議，因此引起了爭議。比提對此回應說，他在該場會議上發表了學術性的演講、且沒提出任何令人反感的言論。2018年8月，白宮發言人{{le|霍根·吉德里|Hogan Gidley}}表示比提已不在白宮工作<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-speechwriter-fired-amid-scrutiny-of-appearance-with-white-nationalists/2018/08/19/f5051b52-a3eb-11e8-a656-943eefab5daf_story.html?|title=Trump speechwriter fired amid scrutiny of appearance with white nationalists|date=2018-08-19|work=Washington Post|accessdate=2021-02-06|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180820110805if_/https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/trump-speechwriter-fired-amid-scrutiny-of-appearance-with-white-nationalists/2018/08/19/f5051b52-a3eb-11e8-a656-943eefab5daf_story.html?utm_term=.231ed1d6a66b|archivedate=2018-08-20}}</ref>。

2019年4月，[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]籍[[聯邦眾議員|聯邦眾議員]][[馬特·蓋茨|馬特·蓋茨]]聘請比提擔任其撰寫講稿的特別顧問<ref name=":0" />。

2020年9月，比提在[[福斯新聞|福斯新聞]][[塔克·卡森|塔克·卡森]]的節目上稱川普的對手正在運用[[顏色革命|顏色革命]]的策略來推翻川普<ref>{{Cite web|title=Darren Beattie: There are ominous similarities between ‘color revolution’ tactics, efforts to oust Trump|url=http://video.foxnews.com/v/6191438294001/|accessdate=2021-02-05|date=2020-09-16|publisher=Fox News|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Deep-state architects of foreign coups behind effort to oust Trump!|url=https://www.wnd.com/2020/09/deep-state-architects-foreign-coups-behind-effort-oust-trump/|accessdate=2021-02-05|author=|date=2020-09-16|publisher=WND|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=WATCH: Darren Beattie Explains the Globalist 'Color Revolution' to Oust President Trump on Tucker Carlson|url=https://bigleaguepolitics.com/watch-darren-beattie-explains-the-globalist-color-revolution-to-oust-president-trump-on-tucker-carlson/|access-date=2022-04-18|date=2020-09-16|work=Big League Politics|language=en-US}}</ref>。

2020年11月，川普任命比提為{{le|美國海外遺產保護委員會|U.S. Commission for the Preservation of America's Heritage Abroad}}成員<ref>{{Cite web|title=2 Coloradans on Trump's list of planned appointments|url=https://www.coloradopolitics.com/news/2-coloradans-on-trumps-list-of-planned-appointments/article_88d770d2-29aa-11eb-aa72-97f30d512ea5.html|accessdate=2021-02-05|date=2020-11-18|publisher=Colorado Politics|language=en}}</ref>。由於比提之前的爭議事件，這項任命遭到[[反誹謗聯盟|反誹謗聯盟]]等團體的反對<ref>{{Cite news|title=Jewish Group Denounces White House Pick for Preservation Commission|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/11/18/us/politics/darren-beattie-holocaust.html|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2020-11-19|accessdate=2021-02-05|language=en-US|first=Maggie|last=Haberman}}</ref>。2022年1月，[[喬·拜登政府|拜登政府]]迫使比提辭去該職務<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trump ally Darren Beattie forced out of federal post by White House after Insider report|url=https://www.businessinsider.in/politics/world/news/trump-ally-darren-beattie-forced-out-of-federal-post-by-white-house-after-insider-report/articleshow/88918443.cms|access-date=2022-04-18|date=2022-01-15|work=Business Insider|language=en}}</ref>。

比提經營的《左輪手槍新聞》暗示[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]特工是引發[[2021年美国国会大厦遭冲击事件|2021年美國國會騷亂]]的幕後黑手。由此，川普在2022年1月9日發表聲明讚許了比提和《左輪手槍新聞》<ref>{{Cite web|title=Trump praises right-wing site that helped to seed the conspiracy theory that the FBI is to blame for the Capitol riot|url=https://www.businessinsider.com/trump-praises-revoler-news-pushed-false-fbi-capitol-riot-theory-2022-1|access-date=2022-04-18|date=2022-01-10|last=Porter|first=Tom|work=Business Insider|language=en-US}}</ref>。

